name: It's a Hard Knock Life.
description:
...But you don't have to accessorize like it is.

Bravely step out into the cold, cruel world wearing these matte silver earrings.  Vintage chain and wire-wrapped "knocker" hang from sterling silver earwires.  Overall length 2".

Knock, knock, knockin'.

$32.00

name: Glitter Snowman.
description:
So this is what happens to Frosty when he has a few too many nips of the eggnog and decides to embrace his feminine side.  Glittery Snowmen.

You can't beat this earring for something festive for the holidays (or anydays) that doesn't overtly scream Christmas!  Graduated, granulated, laser cut stardust beads in either silver or gold.  Sterling silver or 14k gold fill earwires.

Overall length is 1 1/2 inches.

Ho dee ho ho.

$32.00

name: Multifaceted.
description:
You're not one-dimensional.  Nuh uh.  You've got layers...like an onion, right?

You, my friend, are Multifaceted.

The Multifaceted earring has a gorgeous (multifaceted) vintage lucite drop with matching Swarovski crystal.  It comes in clear, topaz, and smoke with sterling silver earwires.  

Explore all of your facets with one in each color.

$32.00

name: This and That
description:
Fabulous vintage goldplated multistrand bracelet is adorned with sparkly lucite gems and and pretties.

7 1/8" in length

$65.00

name: Flower Girl.
description:
Flowers in her hair, flowers everywhere...  Who doesn't love the Flower Girl?  Well, those Cowsill boys sure did.

Flower Girl earrings are everything we all were back in those innocent days...sweet, dependable, and a lot smaller.  The silver and the gold are just different enough from each other that you probably need them both.  Overall length is 1".

Gold with 14k gold fill earwires.  Silver with sterling silver earwires.

And I knew (I knew, I knew, I knew, I knew) that she could make me happy...

$20.00

name: Twiggy.
description:
Not the 60's supermodel, but an earring worthy of one.

Brushed golden balls hang from vintage brass twigs.  14k gold fill earwires.

Overall length is 1 1/4 inch.

name: Holiday Fanfaronade, medium.
description:
Fan-far-o-nade. n. French. : a boasting or flaunting behaviour

My take on this is that a fanfaronade is that time when you feel like tooting your own horn.  You are fabulous and you want everyone to know it!  This earring should make it obvious to everyone you meet.  This medium style is available in Turquoise or Holiday.  Overall length 2 1/2".  

Vintage faceted lucite, moonglow, and sugar glass beads.  Handformed 14k goldfilled earwires.

Holiday Fanfaronade $49.00  

Toot away!

name: Reserved.  -Dog tag necklace
description:
Reserved.

Not your demeanor, your heart.  For that special someone.  

A brushed silver vintage dog tag is topped with a hammered brass heart and a "reserved" tag.  The 2 inch tag hangs from either vintage brass or silver ball chain.

Necklace with silver chain has an overall length of 34 inches, brass is 36 inches.

$46.00

name: Turquoise Fanfaronade, Medium
description:
Fan-far-o-nade. n. French. : a boasting or flaunting behaviour

My take on this is that a fanfaronade is that time when you feel like tooting your own horn.  You are fabulous and you want everyone to know it!  This earring should make it obvious to everyone you meet.  This medium style is available in Turquoise or Holiday.  Overall length 2 1/2".  

Vintage faceted lucite beads and dangles.  Handformed 14k goldfilled earwires.

Turquoise Fanfaronade $49.00  

Toot away!

name: Chex.
description:
Wheat? Corn? Rye?

Metal?  These Chex may not be edible but they are certainly are style-alicious!  Made of vintage metal something or 'nothers that I have hung from handformed sterling silver earwires.

2 1/8" overall length.

$42.00

name: 96 Tears.
description:
Am I the only one who remembers the one-hit wonders   "? and the Mysterions"?  If not, you know where this name came from.  It was number 1 on the Billboard charts the week of October 29, 1966. 

This is the perfect earring for those who like their bling small, classic, and understated or for when you don't have the time to figure out what pair matches your new outfit.  These match everything.  

Vintage matte teardrops with sterling silver earwires.  Overall length is 1 1/4".

You're gonna cry, cry, cry, cry... 
(if these sell out before you buy, buy, buy buy...)

$20.00

name: Lovers.
description:
Vintage lucite faux cameo of lovers is both victorian and goth at the same time.  Old school meet new school.

Adjustable size silverplate band.

$18.00

name: Reserved.  -Heart necklace
description:
Reserved.

Not your demeanor, your heart.  For that special someone.  

A hammered silver heart is topped with a brass open heart and a "reserved" tag.  The 1 1/2 inch charm hangs from a vintage brass ball chain with bronze extender and clasp.

Overall length of 22 inches.

$38.00

name: Be Mine.
description:
Candy hearts are for babies.  Big girls want to wear big girl jewelry.

These dainty little vintage fillagree hearts are the perfect way to ask someone to be yours.  Beautiful goldplated hearts hang from 14k gold fill earwires.

Overall length is 1 inch.

Go ahead and ask.  I'm sure "The Answer Is Yes".

$20.00

name: Guess Who?
description:
Why it's the cutest lil' owl, that's who!

Vintage carved lucite owls with sterling silver beads and earwires.

1" in length.  Available in turquoise and black.

name: Victorian Saucers.
description:
Long, long ago, before there was such a thing as flying saucers, there were Victorian Saucers.  

Harken back to that day by wearing these fabulous earrings with saucer shaped beads.  Vintage etched lucite beads with a sweet heart design and matching Swarovski crystals.  Overall length is 1 3/4".

Gold with 14k goldfill earwires.  Red with sterling silver earwires.

name: Mesh and Pearl.
description:
Simple yet classic vintage mesh bracelet with a pearl clasp.  Oh yes, Audrey would have had one of these.

7 3/4" in length.

$32.00

name: Gone to the Dogs.
description:
A most fabulous collection of rhinestone and pearl encrusted vintage dog charms surround this nice heavy curb link chain.  14k gold fill toggle clasp.

Matching necklaces available.

8 1/2" in length.

$85.00

name: Holly Berry.
description:
Like Halle Berry but Holly Berry...get it?

Oh well, you will want to get the Holly Berry earrings and necklace.  They are beautifully detailed vintage brass with little clusters of glass beaded berries.  The earrings have 14k goldfill earwires and are 2 1/2" long.  The matching necklace is on a 16" vintage gold mesh chain with 14k goldfill lobster clasp.


$38.00

*Necklace sold out*

name: Planetary Alignment.
description:
Sometimes everything lines up.  The moon.  The stars.  The shotglasses on the bar...

But when the planets line up it is magical.

Magical I say.

Magnificent vintage glitter lucite orbs are encaged in brass and dangle in a brass ellipse.  Sterling silver earwires.

$46.00

name: Bullet Bra.
description:
Pulled straight from a 1950's lingerie ad:

The Bullet Bra.

Vintage goldplated conical drop beneath 14k gold fill earwires.

Va, Va, Voom!

$26.00

name: My Beating Heart.
description:
Bestill it.

Can you not control that feeling you get when they are near?  Does your heart start pounding faster and faster?  

Now you can show this on the outside as well.  This vintage gold heart hangs from gold hoops and a 14k gold fill earwire.

Overall length is a petite 1 1/4 inch.  Looks lovely with the matching necklace or any of the Reserved necklaces. 

Thump.  Thump, thump.  THUMPTHUMPTHUMP.

$24.00

name: Butterflies Are Free.
description:
Free to be...

A wonderful Calderesque mobile of dancing butterflies.  Vintage enameled film over goldtone frames.  14k gold fill earwires.

Overall length is 2 1/2".

Flutter by, butterfly.

$30.00

name: La fleur d'or
description:
Golden flowers with a sparkling rhinestone center are connected by mesh pamels.  14k goldfill clasp.

6 3/4" in length.

$45.00

name: Color Wheel.
description:
These necklaces are fun to throw on one at a time or layer.  Vintage faceted lucite or glass charms hang from a 18" vintage brass chain with a beautiful patina.  Handformed brass clasp.

Spin the color wheel!

$38.00

name: Gitarzan.
description:
He's got a girl named Jane with no last name kinda homely and plain but he loves her just the same.

That Gitarzan!  God love him...  

Yet another pair of earrings named after a 60's novelty song.  The Gitarzan is a little 'ol pair of vintage etched anodized aluminum "gitars" that have a sparkly design etched onto their bodies.  They come in cobalt blue, red, green, burgundy, gold, and silver.  Overall length is 1 1/4".  

Gitarzan, he's a gitar man.  He's all you can stand, give him a hand, gitarzan.

$20.00

name: Glimmer Twins.
description:
Keith/Mick or Mick/Keith?  Either way they are the Glimmer Twins.  And like them, the Glimmer Twin earrings know how to deliver.  Sparkle, flash, yes.  But there's substance underneath.  

Vintage glitter embedded drops come in red, purple, silver, and gold.  Overall length 2 1/2".  14k gold fill earwires.

Sometimes, you CAN get what you want.

$30.00

name: ...by any other name.
description:
A rose by any other name would...?

a. Be a daisy.
b. Not be a rose.
c. Smell as sweet.

If you picked c you are technically correct but wouldn't it have been more fun to pick a or b?

Vintage anodized aluminum roses hang from an undulating silver stem.  Sterling silver earwires.  Overall length is 2 inches. Matching necklace with a smaller rose is available in red.

$30.00

name: My Beating Heart. -necklace
description:
Bestill it.

Can you not control that feeling you get when they are near?  Does your heart start pounding faster and faster?  

Now you can show this on the outside as well.  This vintage gold heart rests atop a hammered silver heart base.  The 1 1/2 inch charm hangs from a 20" vintage brass ball chain with a bronze extender and clasp. 

Thump.  Thump.  THUMPTHUMPTHUMP.

$38.00

name: Lollipops.
description:
Don't lick the earrings! 

Fabulous large vintage faceted lucite crystals with matching Swarovski crystals that look good enough to eat.  Handformed sterling silver earwires.  Overall length is 1 3/4"

Available in clear, red, green, cobalt blue, and purple.

Slurp.

$38.00

name: See me, Hear me.
description:
Why the name?  I don't know.  These kind of remind me of ears or eyes or I was listening to the Who's Tommy when I made them.

Vintage matte silver with sterling earwires.  Length is 1 3/4".

...touch me, heal me.

$26.00

name: Ball Drop.
description:
You are standing in Times Square.  It's almost midnight.  You will soon be locking lips with someone you love or just met. You have to look your sparkly best so of course you are wearing your Ball Drop earrings.

Long a uttal bestseller, the Ball Drops have fantastical clear vintage lucite balls with gold or silver filaments swimming inside.  They are like a party in a bead!  

14k gold fill or sterling silver earwires.  Overall length is 2 1/2".

Also available as a necklace on a 16" sterling or 14k goldfill chain.

10,9,8,7,6....

$45.00

name: Roaring 20's.
description:
They came, they roared, they conquered.

And you can too when you wear these snazzy earbobs.  Vintage onyx faceted crystals dangle from 14k gold fill earwires.

$34.00

name: Twinkle Bracelet.
description:
This twinkly little bracelet is the perfect one to dress up or down, wear alone or in a group, with a fox or in a box.

Vintage anodized aluminum discs are laser cut to reveal their inner shine.  Affixed to a rhodium plated link bracelet with a silverplate foldover clasp to make it easy to get on and off by yourself.

Available in twinkly round black, red/black oval, or multicolor/oval (black, red, green, and blue).

Length is 7 1/4".

$38.00

name: In Orbit.
description:
Fasten those seat belts, we're going In Orbit!

This fun and funky ring features a 15mm lucite orb encircled by a brass ring.  Shank is made of goldplated wire.  Please make sure to select your ring size.  Custom made to order.

Wow, space travel is fun.

Last one!  Available in size 8.5 only.

$26.00

name: Hoop it Up!
description:
Vintage faux tortoise shell hoops hang from brass chains.  14k gold fill earwires.

$30.00

name: Walking Stick.
description:
As Bill Withers so accurately said, sometimes we all need somebody to lean on.  If you're having one of those days, just pop in your Walking Sticks and Voila!, instant support.

The Walking sticks are long, lean, powerful vintage lucite beads with some Czech glass and Swarovski crystals for added umph.  Overall length is 3 1/2".

Teal and blue sticks with sterling earwires.
Frosted crystal and tortoise sticks on 14k goldfill earwires.

Just call on me brother.

$30.00

name: Ice Chips.
description:
Colorful chips off the old block of ice, these are.

Wonderful vintage lucite chips hang from either silver or goldplated chain.  The pebbly surface reminds me of the faux stained glass that was popular in the 60's.

14k goldfill or sterling silver earwires.  Overall length of all is approximately 2 3/4" however the size of the chips are different.  Green is the smallest at 1/2", red and blue are 1", and the dark amber is 1 1/4".

Brrrr.

$30.00

name: Triangular.
description:
That about covers it.

Colorful vintage lucite triangles hang from sterling silver earwires.  Tiny l'il things that are not quite 1" long.

They come in an opaque light turquoise and a darker translucent aquamarine.  

Not oblong.  Not spheroid.  

Triangular.

$16.00

name: Tripod.
description:
Good things come in threes.  Triplets.  Little pigs.  Blind mice.  Stooges.  Guitar chords in punk songs....

And the Tripod earring.  It's got three shiny silver legs to stand on.  Handformed sterling silver earwire.  Overall length is 2 3/4".

Peas in a pod....

$42.00

name: Let it Go.
description:
You know, sometimes it's just not worth fighting over.  You've got to pick your battles.  Throw in the towel.  Release it to the universe.  Just Let it Go.

A vintage goldplated teardrop or marquise swings from golden chain.  14k gold fill earwires.  Overall length is 2 1/2".

See, you feel better already.

$32.00

name: Fanfaronade.
description:
Fan-far-o-nade. n. French. : a boasting or flaunting behaviour

My take on this is that a fanfaronade is that time when you feel like tooting your own horn.  You are fabulous and you want everyone to know it!  This earring should make it obvious to everyone you meet.  This large style is available in Classic Pearl or Tiger.  Overall length 3".  

Vintage lucite and glass beads.  Handformed 14k goldfilled earwires.

Toot away!

$52.00

name: Buckle Up!
description:
The world is nothing but possibilities.  Everything is new, fresh, exciting.  You're definitely along for the ride but caution says perhaps you should Buckle Up!

Beautiful vintage lucite amber-toned buckle is securely fastened with a sterling silver wrap to a handformed sterling earwire.

Overall length is 3".

The ride is half the fun.  Enjoy!

$42.00

name: Date Night.
description:
You get the call.  Friday at 8.  Dinner and maybe a movie after?  You don't know if it's going to be someplace fancy schmanchy or casual.  So to play it safe you go basic with the clothes but you let your earrings say it's something special.  The Date Night.  Problem solved.

Date Night earrings are vintage tin cut faceted German glass with matching Swarovski crystals for extra sparkle.  Light green version has faceted lucite instead of glass.  Handformed sterling silver earwires.  Overall length 2 1/2".  

Available in sapphire blue, aquamarine, clear, jet black, light green and smoke.

$42.00

name: Kinetic.
description:
You're a mover.  You're a shaker.  You know it, they know it, your earring knows it too.

Kinetic earrings are made to move with you.  Awesome vintage beads on goldplated or sterling silver wire.  Sterling silver or 14k goldfill hoops.  Overall length is 2 1/2".  

If you're not moving, you're not going anywhere.

$42.00

name: Victorian Snowflakes.
description:
I just love the delicate look of these vintage brass snowflakes.  The only thing that could possibly make them any prettier would be to add a sparkly tiny sapphire Swarovski crystal to their centers.  

So I did. 

Vintage brass, Swarovski crystals, and 14k goldfill earwires.  Overall length is 1 1/4 inch.

Let it snow.

$28.00

name: Surf's Up!
description:
Depending on where you live you may not be thinking about surfing right now but that was certainly my first thought when I came across these fabulous vintage brass pieces. 

So put on your surfboard earrings and think summer.  14k gold fill earwires.  Overall length 3 3/4 ".  

As we say here in Kentucky...cowabunga y'all.

$36.00
